<ol id="fs-id2267127" type="a">
<li>is supported by the annular ligament</li>
<li>contains an articular disc that strongly unites the bones</li>
<li>is supported by the ulnar collateral ligament</li>
<li>is a hinge joint that allows for flexion/extension of the forearm</li>
</ol>
