<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id2094763">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id2094765"><p id="fs-id2094766">Which region of the vertebral column has the <em data-effect="italics">greatest </em>range of motion for rotation?</p>
<ol id="fs-id1483037" type="a">
